values: So far so good.Spring break has been pretty cool, except the part where i had to see Ben in the act, other than that, its been all good.I had to work the first couple of days of spring break, got to hang out with Jonny V., Zach, and Adam which was fun.The other days i didnt really do anything before work.Yesterday was cool, Ben stayed over, and we sat around for awile.I had to go up to the bank and take out some cash, then danielle and nikki came by it was really cool.Later we went up to the mall and i ate to many fries from that chiken place.The week is over and it really pisses me off, school is shitty.Why should i have to wake up to goto a place that pisses me off?I guess its just the way things work.I just figured id update so everyone knew what was going on.lata

Spring break is almost here....its gonna be a week of much need time away from school.Only i always have work and that sucks, but i have four days off during spring break all in a row.They are gonna be fun whether people like it or not.Pride week is going on in school...god i wanna shoot myself, i got yelled at by a bunch of black girls because they hate white people.I have no problem with them.O well, this journal entry is the first with my new cd burner installed,YES!i have a whole lot of shit on my mind, but i cant seem to get it out onto this thing,so im just gonna go now.Check back,maybe i'll get it.

Alright, went to CZW saturday.The only two words i can think of to describe it is fucking awesome.The match's were crazy and Sonja almost became the Best Of The Best, but he was one match short.It was a fucking great show.Before the show, we went to friendlys, the new home of pre-czw eating, and we ate and hit on our waitress.It was definately a great guys night out.I think that the friendly's trip wouldnt have been complete with the pretime smoke....it made the trip.Sunday....was a whole lot of working and i was sooooo tired because i didnt goto sleep till like 4 and had to be in work at 10ish.o well i made it through.Today was just school then four of the shittiest hours of work ever.aight im out lata.

Quotes of T-Roy:

this is me during the night at troys house,we have all been retarded..oddly justin sane the most normal of the night....ironic?the night has been full of old wrestling tapes, vice city, and troys insanity....pure insanity.we have gone from ready for best of the best to being ready to get some action.this is crazy...and now anyone who reads this must post, why even come and read my journal if you not gonna tell me how im doing with it.SO POST BITCHES.aight im out.lata
    east coast rep.

Ladies and gentleman,boys and girls, children of all ages.I am here tonight to present a live journal entry.Hey all...its me again, the only person who posts in this thing, considering its mine!Tonight wasn't to bad, went with my pops for a little while
then it was off to have some BBCL fun.We went up to jp's and chilled for a little bit,oh what fun that was.Then we took off to some shitty talent show where there were a lot of half naked Delran girls performing.You would think it was exciting considering they were half naked, but they were Delran girls and it definately wasn't exciting.We hung out there for a little bit and met up with Adam and Frank.Then took off for the final ours of our shit filled night.We ended up at the Dynasty, where tons of odd/humorous things occured.I mean from Adam making his titties bounce to watching this kid eat fries with cheese,gravy, and ketchup.Possibly the grossing thing i have seen in a long time.We had some laughs,tears were shed, but at the end of the night,when all the dirt had cleared, it turned out to be a pretty fun diner trip.Thats about all i have to say about my day.Wow kids, wasnt that exciting?IM OUT MUTHA FUCKA'S.
 LATA

The only thing that can explain what im thinking is
    ViEw82: Sat APRIL 12th is now known as "THE DAY OF WRESTLING"

this saturday is best of the best.its gonna be fucking nuts.we are gonna try and get some match's in earlier on in the day only to goto one(maybe two) wrestling events that night.its gonna be crazy.CZW CZW. anywho, on a different note, work still sucks and for those of you without a job i have only one thing to say to you....DONT GET ONE.it sucks worse than rosie o donnell having that tv show....i mean what was she thinking?LETS SHOOT KOOSH BALLS IN THE STANDS....THAT'LL BRING A CROWD.well thats all i have to say,im suprised i am updating so soon,maybe its because i have nothing better to do when no one is on fucking line!im out

yo fuckers, i got one now, look out! well this is it, dont expect a lot of posts and dont fuck with me on my journal thing, cause if thats what you want to do,you cant be a very cool person if you have that much time.so until next time, this is butch signing off.
  east coast rep.
